{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UW5Au2yfo5zp8cBrq7ye6k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011DVF2gVvXeZhm9fFCEseqF","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","old_string":"```\ncloche init [--workflow <name>] [--image <base>]\n```\n\n| Flag | Default | Description |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n| `--image <base>` | `ubuntu:24.04` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n\nCreates `.cloche/` with a workflow file, Dockerfile, configuration file\n(`config.toml`), and prompt templates (`implement.md`, `fix.md`,\n`update-docs.md`). Skips files that already exist.\nAlso adds gitignore entries for runtime state directories.","new_string":"```\ncloche init [--workflow <name>] [--base-image <image>]\n```\n\n| Flag | Default | Description |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n| `--base-image <image>` | `cloche-base:latest` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n\nCreates `.cloche/` with a workflow file, Dockerfile, configuration file\n(`config.toml`), prompt templates (`implement.md`, `fix.md`,\n`update-docs.md`), a `version` file (starting at `1`), an orchestration\nworkflow (`host.cloche`), and a prompt generation script\n(`scripts/prepare-prompt.sh`). Skips files that already exist.\nAlso adds gitignore entries for runtime state directories."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1382,"cache_read_input_tokens":57742,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1382},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7a15993-19ea-4872-bb6e-c0a2